<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vanquish</title>
    <!-- add google font -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/265ed8ed5a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Yanone+Kaffeesatz:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="normalize.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <aside>

        <img src="logo.PNG" alt="logo" class="logo">

        <section class="details">
            <!-- project explanation -->
            <h3 class="fancy">What is Vanquish?</h3>
            <p>What do you want to conquer in life? Vanquish is a tool that visitors can use to record their dreams and
                wants out of life. Do you want to experience something? Learn something? Participate in an extroidinary
                event? Vanquish is serves as a home for your dreams to transform into reality.</p>
            <h3 class="fancy">How do I use Vanquish?</h3>
            <p>Post your conquer goal to the board. Come back to complete it later. You can still view your conquered
                goals until you're ready to clean up shop and get more goals on the board. Add a creative screen name to
                unqiuely label your </p>
        </section>

        <section class="submit">
            <!-- form -->
            <h3 class="fancy">Submit your future</h3>
            <form action="/dreams" method="post">
                <div>
                    <label class="label" for="name">Enter your screen name:</label><br>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="screen name" name="name" required>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="dream" class="label">Enter your goal:</label><br>
                    <textarea type="text" placeholder="Write your dream to conquer here" cols="30" rows="10"
                        name="dream" required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit">Post</button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="social">
            <!-- professional links/footer stuff -->
            <ul class="dos">
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i> Visit my <a href="https://aharleydev.netlify.app/"
                        target="_blank">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i> Follow me on <a href="https://twitter.com/DevHarleyA"
                        target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
            </ul>
            <small>&copy; HarleyADev 2022</small>
        </section>

    </aside>
    <main>
        <section class="goals">
            <!-- have the results populate in separate divs here (post its)  -->
            <h3 class="header">Dreams</h3>
            <ul class="dreams">
                <% for (let i=0; i < dreams.length; i++ ) {%>
                    <li class="dream">
                        <p>
                            <%= dreams[i].name %>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <%= dreams[i].dream %>
                        </p>
                        <span>Start Date: </span><span>
                            <%= dreams[i].startDate.slice(3,15) %>
                        </span>
                        <span class="icons">
                            <span>Delete: </span><span><i class="fa-solid fa-ban fa-xl"></i> <span>Conquered: </span>
                            </span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check fa-xl"></i></span>
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <% } %>
            </ul>

        </section>
        <section class="completed">
            <h3 class="header">Conquers</h3>
            <ul class="conquers">
                <% for (let i=0; i < conquer.length; i++ ) {%>
                    <li class="dream">
                        <p>
                            <%= conquer[i].name %>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <%= conquer[i].dream %>
                        </p>
                        <span>Completed Date: </span><span>
                            <%= conquer[i].completedDate.slice(3,15) %>
                        </span>
                        <span class="icons">
                            <span>Delete: </span><span><i class="fa-solid fa-ban fa-xl"></i> <span>Conquered: </span>
                            </span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check fa-xl"></i></span>
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <% } %>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <!-- Features: (Post) a bucket list item, mark it complete (update) & add date (update), and (delete) the task to make room for more -->
    </main>

    <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>